    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic wear. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are solid, though you should expect some minor oil seepage and aging suspension components that may need attention soon. The exterior has visible clear coat peeling on the roof and a few door dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and a cracked dashboard. It is a functional, honest car that starts every time and is priced to reflect its current state.",
