    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with this absolute beauty, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one\u2014not a scratch or a smudge in sight. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
