    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, maintained to an exacting standard. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring six individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring OEM bushings and dampers for precise turn-in and lateral stability. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The exterior finish and interior upholstery show no signs of degradation, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous mechanical stewardship. A true turn-key analog masterpiece for the performance-oriented purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
