      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously garaged and pampered since day one, featuring flawless original paint with a deep, mirror-like finish and an interior that still carries that new-car scent. Every surface, from the supple, uncreased leather seats to the pristine alloy wheels, is free of blemishes. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history with every milestone met ahead of schedule. There are zero scratches, zero dents, and zero compromises. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
